        <updateDate>2010-11-09T16:08:47Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Fairness in Unemployment Act - Amends the Supplemental Appropriations Act, 2008 to revise the formula for determining if a state is in an extended benefit period.</p> <p>Modifies the threshold rates of unemployment that must be met by a state in order to establish eligibility for Tier-4 emergency unemployment compensation (EUC) for such state.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
